      <h2>By: Anna Deavere Smith</h2>
      <div class="stars">
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star-half-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      </div>
      <p>Anna walked me home last night. She was very friendly! And were both Annas so fuck yea</p>
    </article>
    <article class="review">
      <h2>By: Somebody else</h2>
      <div class="stars">
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <i class="fa fa-star-half-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      </div>
      <p>Wicked walking buddy</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</form>
</div>
